Package: Kuresi
Type: Package
Title: Competitive fitness of Cancer clones
Description: Kuresi is an R package for analyzing competitive 
  fitness between cancer clones in single cell and spatial transcriptomics data. 
  It provides tools to compute and visualize competition scores based on differential gene expression patterns.
Author: Patrick C.N. Martin <patrick.martin@cshs.org>
Version: 0.0.1
Maintainer: Patrick C.N. Martin <patrick.martin@cshs.org>
